page.title: 12THE FISH & CHIP SHOP
page.content: The Fish and chip shop in Ranskill opens every day except Sunday Monday and Tuesday night.It opens at 11.30 AM till 1.30 PM at lunch and 7.30 PM till 11.30 PM at night. The most popular meal is Fish and chips. They sell Chips,Fish,Beans,Fish cakes, Peas,Sausages,Gravy,Mussels,Pies,Chick en,Scampi,Soft drinks and vinegar . Saturday night is the best night for making money. The shop is not very big .The shop is about 14 Years old.There is no where to sit, like tables and chairs .The Fish Shop is next to a shop which sells sweets and papers.A meal of fish and chips costs Â£1.14 which isn"t much money.
